metadata.name: Neptune
metadata.description:
Neptune is named for the Roman god of sea, who is identified with the Greek deity Poseidon.

Neptune is the psychic planet of ideals, intuition, spirituality and compassion, the domain of dreams and delusions.

This is how Neptune planet's texture would look like to me.

So welcome to Neptune..

Acrylic on canvas

120x70

Original canvas will be sent to the address of the owner.
